SELECT "DbT1001HihokenshaDaicho".* FROM rgdb."DbT1001HihokenshaDaicho" AS "DbT1001HihokenshaDaicho" INNER JOIN (SELECT "hihokenshaNo", MAX("idoYMD"||"edaNo") AS max FROM rgdb."DbT1001HihokenshaDaicho" WHERE "hihokennshaKubunCode" = '1' AND "logicalDeletedFlag" = FALSE AND "ichigoShikakuShutokuYMD" <= #{資格基準日} AND ("shikakuSoshitsuYMD" IS NULL OR #{資格基準日}<= "shikakuSoshitsuYMD")
AND ("koikinaiJushochiTokureiFlag" ='1' AND "koikinaiTokureiSochimotoShichosonCode" IN #{市町村コード} ) OR ("koikinaiJushochiTokureiFlag" ='0' AND "koikinaiTokureiSochimotoShichosonCode" IN #{市町村コード} )
GROUP BY "hihokenshaNo") AS B ON "DbT1001HihokenshaDaicho"."hihokenshaNo" = B."hihokenshaNo" AND ("DbT1001HihokenshaDaicho"."idoYMD" || "DbT1001HihokenshaDaicho"."edaNo") = B.max
